Package nl.naturalis.geneious

Class StoredDocument

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.naturalis.geneious.StoredDocument
  • public class StoredDocument
extends Object
    A wrapper around the Geneious-native AnnotatedPluginDocument class with all of its Naturalis-specific annotations pre-fetched into a NaturalisNote instance. A StoredDocument has presumably been retrieved through some database query and upon instantiation is exactly like the database record. As the operation proceeds the NaturalisNote instance may get updated, and, if so, will be saved back to the document.
